@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
[*] --> Closed
Closed --> Cancelled : process
Cancelled --> Created : submit
Created --> Delivered : update
Created : entry / log statement
Delivered --> Approved : process
Approved --> [*]
@enduml